Your vhdl code is in 
	vhdl/

The testbench VHDL code is in
	vhdl_tb/

The C testbench code is in 
	tb/

Run
	. build_ghdl_tb.sh

to build the testbench.

Run
	. build_ghdl_model.sh

to build the simulator executable.


To run the simulation
   1. open one shell in which you type
        ./bin/testbench_vhdl

   2. open another shell in which you
	type
	
	./switch_2x2_test_bench --wave=run.ghw

	you can omit the run.ghw if you wish.

   A log of the run (highlighting errors if
   any) will be generated by the testbench.


